	(text "USB FS: D+/D- direct to PA12/PA11 - no series Rs needed (AN4879).\nA/B data pairs joined on the 16P receptacle footprint.\nOptional: USBLC6-2SC6 ESD array across D+/D-/VBUS."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30.48 302.26 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
		)
		(uuid "18fee401-c800-4bf8-b061-f1f5e6bc016a")
	)
	(text "ELRS/CRSF receiver on UART1 (5V supplied!).\nSpare: UART3, USART6, I2C1 (future baro/mag).\nI2C1 needs 2.2k-4.7k pull-ups only when used - on the breakout board."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 414.02 124.46 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
		)
		(uuid "2ca42c84-3249-4ebb-bb6f-efc0e773d391")
	)
	(text "IMU on dedicated TLV733P rail. 100nF at VDD + VDDIO pins.\nR10 = CS pull-up (no floating CS in DFU). Board center, away from LDO heat.\nRESV pins left open here - confirm handling vs DS-000347 pin table before layout."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 297.18 186.7 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
		)
		(uuid "69370901-a4ac-48c3-a330-748da2277f6a")
	)
	(text "BOOT0 button + R1 pull-down = DFU entry.\nR2 on PB2/BOOT1 keeps DFU deterministic (AN2606)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30.48 193.04 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
		)
		(uuid "9a11cd1f-6501-4efb-a16a-768a8f9e1f8a")
	)
	(text "Decoupling: one 100nF per VDD pin + 4.7uF bulk; 1uF+10nF at VDDA;\n100nF at MCU VBAT. C20/C21 = MANDATORY VCAP caps, place at pins 31/47."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30.48 116.98 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
		)
		(uuid "b77b8a33-e2ca-44e2-9bb3-5f28fd1d13cc")
	)
	(text "!! ESC PINOUT = CANDIDATE ONLY - bench-verify the Raptor BLS-04 harness\nwith a multimeter BEFORE layout (see FC_audit_2026-06-09.md C1).\nMotor order S1-S4 is remapped in config.h, not in copper.\nVBAT divider 100k/10k -> PC1 (scale 110). CRT: 1k + 3V3 zener -> PC2."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 304.8 22.86 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
		)
		(uuid "baf80eb5-61da-48f2-83be-b58770e81358")
	)
	(text "BZ1 = 5V ACTIVE magnetic buzzer (BF beeper is on/off GPIO).\nR13 stops boot-time chatter. Set BEEPER_INVERTED to match at bring-up.\nStatus LED on PB8 (PC13 forbidden: 3mA power-switch domain)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 391.16 212.1 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
		)
		(uuid "d4097f8e-3202-40f4-a124-4e38e303bd8b")
	)
	(text "CUSTOM BETAFLIGHT FC v3 - STM32F405RGT6 + ICM-42688-P + W25Q128 - 2026-06-09\nGenerated label-net schematic: every net is a global label; rearrange freely in KiCad.\nERC note: power nets driven via labels -> add PWR_FLAG on +5V/+3V3/+3V3_IMU/GND to silence ERC."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
